text: Brandon McKinney (born August 24, 1983 in Dayton, Ohio) is an American football nose tackle for the Indianapolis Colts of the National Football League (NFL). McKinney didn't get drafted but played college football at Michigan State University. McKinney started his NFL career with the San Diego Chargers in 2006 and played 3 seasons with them before signing a contract with the Baltimore Ravens on October 8, 2008. He played four seasons with the Ravens before signing with the Indianapolis Colts on April 4, 2012. ==Other websites== *Brandon McKinney at nfl.com Category:1983 births Category:American football defensive tackles Category:Sportspeople from Ohio Category:Baltimore Ravens players Category:Indianapolis Colts players Category:Living people Category:San Diego Chargers players
